OL,3,CThe Body Shop's new owners look to
OL,4,C'revive' brand after buy out
OL,6,FThe Body Shop has been rescued from
OL,7,Fadministration by a consortium led by
OL,8,FBritish tycoon Mike Jatania, with
OL,9,Fremaining stores to continue trading.
OL,11,FMr Jatania's investment firm Aurea
OL,12,Fannounced the completion of the
OL,13,Facquisition on Saturday.
OL,15,FIt is currently understood there are
OL,16,Fno immediate plans to shut any of The
OL,17,FBody Shop's 116 remaining UK stores.
