OL,3,CThe Body Shop's new owners look to
OL,4,C'revive' brand after buy out
OL,6,FMr Jatania and Charles Denton, former
OL,7,Fchief executive of beauty brand Molton
OL,8,FBrown, will head the new leadership
OL,9,Fteam.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Aurea said the
OL,12,Facquisition was its largest
OL,13,Ftransaction to date and it would
OL,14,F"steer The Body Shop's revival and
OL,15,Freclaim its global leadership in the
OL,16,Fethical beauty sector it pioneered".
