OL,3,CThe Body Shop's new owners look to
OL,4,C'revive' brand after buy out
OL,6,FMr Jatania previously ran Lornamead `
OL,7,Fthe owner of personal care brands
OL,8,Fincluding Lypsyl, Woods of Windsor,
OL,9,FYardley and Harmony haircare ` which
OL,10,Fhe sold to rival Li & Fung for around
OL,11,F#155 million more than 10 years ago.
OL,13,FThe Body Shop fell into administration
OL,14,Fin early February after previous
OL,15,Fforecasts for how much funding it
OL,16,Fwould need to keep going proved too
OL,17,Flow.
