OL,3,CThe Body Shop's new owners look to
OL,4,C'revive' brand after buy out
OL,6,FIn the weeks that followed,
OL,7,Fadministrators said hundreds of jobs
OL,8,Fwould be lost and dozens of shops
OL,9,Fclosed.
OL,11,FThe business had employed about 1,500
OL,12,Fstore workers before the
OL,13,Fadministration.
OL,15,FThe Body Shop was founded in 1976 by
OL,16,FDame Anita Roddick, trading out of a
OL,17,Fsmall shop in Brighton originally and
OL,18,Fmade its name selling cruelty-free
OL,19,Ffairtrade products.
