OL,3,CThe Body Shop's new owners look to
OL,4,C'revive' brand after buy out
OL,6,FMr Jatania, co-founder of Aurea, said:
OL,7,F"With The Body Shop, we have acquired
OL,8,Fa truly iconic brand with highly
OL,9,Fengaged consumers in over 70 markets
OL,10,Faround the world.
OL,12,F"We plan to focus relentlessly on
OL,13,Fexceeding their expectations by
OL,14,Finvesting in product innovation and
OL,15,Fseamless experiences across all of the
OL,16,Fchannels where customers shop while
OL,17,Fpaying homage to the brand's ethical
OL,18,Fand activist positioning."
